title: Divisional Round Breakdown, LSU-Clemson Preview, Brian Stumpf Interview
itunes:title: Divisional Round Breakdown, LSU-Clemson Preview, Brian Stumpf Interview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss the upcoming Divisional Playoff games: Vikings-49ers (2:00), Titans-Ravens (7:55), Texans-Chiefs (16:55), Seahawks-Packers (22:00). Plus, the guys preview Monday’s College Football Playoff National Championship between LSU and Clemson (26:40). Then, DJ and Bucky are joined by Brian Stumpf, President of Student Sports, on the Elite 11 and The Opening high school football circuit (32:10). DJ briefly talks about his top offensive and defensive rookies of 2019 (48:10). To close the show, the guys answer some fan questions from Apple Podcasts (49:50).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
